# ===== About Page =====
msgid "关于我们"
msgstr "About Us"

msgid "您身边的专业科研助手"
msgstr "Your Professional Research Assistant"

msgid "公司简介"
msgstr "Company Profile"

msgid "广州三君科技有限公司成立于 2022 年，是一家专注于动物实验及配套技术服务的科技型中小企业。"
msgstr "Guangzhou Sengene Technology Co., Ltd was established in 2022, a technology-based SME focusing on animal experiments and supporting technical services."

msgid "核心团队由生物医药背景的博士与资深科研技术人员组成，具备多年的动物模型构建、动物行为学检测、生物信息学分析及数据统计经验，能够为基础研究与转化医学提供一体化技术支持。"
msgstr "Our core team consists of PhDs and senior researchers in biomedicine with years of experience in animal model construction, behavioral testing, bioinformatics analysis, and statistical analysis."

msgid "公司以「用数据说话、以技术赋能科研」为理念，持续打磨标准化实验流程与质量控制体系，助力科研项目高质量产出。"
msgstr "Guided by the philosophy of \"data-driven, technology-empowered research\", we continuously refine standardized experimental procedures and quality control systems."

msgid "服务内容"
msgstr "Our Services"

msgid "动物模型构建：覆盖神经系统、循环系统、运动系统等常用疾病与功能模型。"
msgstr "Animal model construction: covering neurological, circulatory, and musculoskeletal disease models."

msgid "动物行为学与形态学检测：提供记忆学习、焦虑抑郁、运动协调等多维度评估方案。"
msgstr "Behavioral and morphological testing: multi-dimensional assessment including memory, anxiety, and motor coordination."

msgid "动物饲养托管：支持 SPF 级与清洁级动物饲养环境及日常健康监测。"
msgstr "Animal housing: SPF-grade and clean-grade animal housing with daily health monitoring."

msgid "生物信息学分析：涵盖转录组、宏基因组、单细胞测序等多组学数据分析与可视化报告输出。"
msgstr "Bioinformatics analysis: transcriptomics, metagenomics, single-cell sequencing analysis and visualization."

msgid "我们的优势"
msgstr "Our Advantages"

msgid "三君科技与多所高校及科研机构建立了长期合作关系，拥有多项自主知识产权与成熟技术方案，构建了较为完整的动物实验技术链条。"
msgstr "We have established long-term partnerships with universities and research institutions, with proprietary intellectual property and mature technical solutions."

msgid "公司依托标准化 SPF 动物房、行为学实验平台以及生物信息计算平台，打造从实验设计、模型构建到数据分析与结果解读的一站式科研技术服务体系，为客户提供高质量、可重复、可追溯的科研支撑。"
msgstr "Built on standardized SPF animal facilities, behavioral testing platforms, and bioinformatics computing platforms, we provide a one-stop research service system."

msgid "通过专业团队、规范流程与严格质控，三君科技致力于成为科研工作者可信赖的长期合作伙伴。"
msgstr "With professional teams, standardized procedures, and strict quality control, Sengene is committed to being a reliable long-term partner for researchers."

# ===== Service Page =====
msgid "动物饲养 · 模型构建 · 检测评估 · 数据分析"
msgstr "Animal Housing · Model Construction · Testing & Evaluation · Data Analysis"

msgid "动物饲养平台"
msgstr "Animal Housing Platform"

msgid "SPF 动物房"
msgstr "SPF Animal Facility"

msgid "动物房位于番禺石楼创新科技园内，配备超过 500 个小鼠 IVC 饲养笼位和 150 个大鼠 IVC 饲养笼位，屏障系统内设有独立动物实验室，可满足部分手术操作及行为学检测需求。"
msgstr "Located in Panyu Shilou Innovation Technology Park, equipped with 500+ mouse IVC cages and 150 rat IVC cages. The barrier system includes independent animal laboratories for surgical operations and behavioral testing."

msgid "通过标准化饲养流程和环境监测，保障实验动物健康与实验数据的稳定性，为课题组提供可靠的基础平台。"
msgstr "Standardized feeding procedures and environmental monitoring ensure animal health and data stability."

msgid "神经系统模型"
msgstr "Neurological Models"

msgid "CSR 神经根型颈椎病模型"
msgstr "CSR Cervical Radiculopathy Model"

msgid "造模要点"
msgstr "Key Points"

msgid "通过暴露 C7–T1 椎板并经椎管平行插入特制聚酰胺卡压线，使其位于 C5–T1 神经根处，实现对神经根的持续卡压，稳定复制神经根型颈椎病病理状态。"
msgstr "By exposing the C7-T1 lamina and inserting a polyamide compression line through the spinal canal at the C5-T1 nerve roots, sustained compression is achieved to replicate cervical radiculopathy."

msgid "模型检测 · 周期"
msgstr "Assessment & Duration"

msgid "支持步态评分、步态模式分析、MRI 定位及 HE 染色等多指标评估，实验周期约 7–14 天。"
msgstr "Gait scoring, gait pattern analysis, MRI positioning, and HE staining. Duration: 7-14 days."

msgid "MCAO 大脑中动脉闭塞模型"
msgstr "MCAO Middle Cerebral Artery Occlusion Model"

msgid "在大鼠颈部暴露颈总、颈外及颈内动脉，经颈内动脉插入特定直径线栓，暂时闭塞大脑中动脉，通过控制缺血与再灌注时间模拟脑缺血损伤。"
msgstr "Exposing the common, external, and internal carotid arteries, inserting a filament through the internal carotid to temporarily occlude the middle cerebral artery, simulating ischemic injury."

msgid "可采用 TTC 染色、Longa 评分等方式进行脑梗死范围与神经功能缺损评估，实验周期约 3 天。"
msgstr "TTC staining, Longa scoring for infarct size and neurological deficit assessment. Duration: ~3 days."

msgid "运动系统模型"
msgstr "Musculoskeletal Models"

msgid "KOA 膝骨关节炎模型"
msgstr "KOA Knee Osteoarthritis Model"

msgid "在膝关节腔注射Ⅱ 型胶原蛋白酶溶液，间隔给药诱导关节软骨退变及炎症反应，形成膝骨关节炎样病理改变。"
msgstr "Intra-articular injection of type II collagenase solution to induce cartilage degeneration and inflammation, forming knee osteoarthritis-like pathology."

msgid "支持 microCT、HE 及番红固绿染色等结构与病理评估，实验周期约 35–42 天。"
msgstr "MicroCT, HE and Safranin O/Fast Green staining for structural and pathological assessment. Duration: 35-42 days."

msgid "ACLT 前交叉韧带横断模型"
msgstr "ACLT Anterior Cruciate Ligament Transection Model"

msgid "采用吸入麻醉后在膝关节内侧入路，暴露并剪断前交叉韧带，通过 Lachman 试验证实断离，建立关节不稳定导致的继发骨关节炎模型。"
msgstr "Using inhalation anesthesia, medial knee approach to expose and transect the ACL, confirmed by Lachman test, establishing secondary osteoarthritis model."

msgid "通过 microCT、HE 与番红固绿染色对骨与软骨损伤程度进行综合评估，实验周期约 28–56 天。"
msgstr "MicroCT, HE and Safranin O/Fast Green staining for bone and cartilage damage assessment. Duration: 28-56 days."

