msgstr "Open field, water maze, behavioral calibration and memory testing for mice/rats with multi-channel automated data collection."

msgid "行为学平台 · 软硬件支持"
msgstr "Behavioral Platform · Hardware & Software"

msgid "IVC 动物饲养系统"
msgstr "IVC Animal Housing System"

msgid "提供高标准屏障级 IVC 笼具及配套通风过滤系统，适合长期动物实验与清洁度要求较高的项目，支持小规模试验至规模化饲养的不同场景。"
msgstr "High-standard barrier-level IVC cages with ventilation and filtration systems for long-term animal experiments."

msgid "SPF 饲养 · 环境控制"
msgstr "SPF Housing · Environmental Control"

msgid "动物实验及测序相关试剂盒"
msgstr "Reagent Kits for Animal Experiments & Sequencing"

msgid "自营品牌 AngieGan 及联合研发品牌 ECOTOP，提供动物实验配套试剂盒、组织形态学染色试剂、分子生物学检测试剂盒以及部分转录组 / 宏基因组预处理试剂，帮助课题组快速搭建实验体系。"
msgstr "Own brand AngieGan and co-developed brand ECOTOP. Reagent kits for animal experiments, histology, molecular biology, and sequencing."

msgid "试剂耗材 · 多品牌合作"
msgstr "Reagents & Consumables · Multi-brand"

